e></figure><p>快捷键：ctrl+shift+K</p><blockquote><p>本快捷键与搜狗输入法的软键盘快捷键冲突</p></blockquote><p>右键—&gt;插入—&gt;代码块并在右下角补充代码规则</p><figure class="highlight jsp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
